FLAML::::.github/workflows/python-package.yml::::jobs::::build::::steps::::steps_2::::name::::If mac, install libomp to facilitate lgbm and xgboost install

FLAML::::.github/workflows/python-package.yml::::jobs::::build::::steps::::steps_2::::run::::# remove libomp version constraint after xgboost works with libomp>11.1.0
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/homebrew-core/679923b4eb48a8dc7ecc1f05d06063cd79b3fc00/Formula/libomp.rb -O $(find $(brew --repository) -name libomp.rb)
brew install libomp
export CC=/usr/bin/clang
export CXX=/usr/bin/clang++
export CPPFLAGS="$CPPFLAGS -Xpreprocessor -fopenmp"
export CFLAGS="$CFLAGS -I/usr/local/opt/libomp/include"
export CXXFLAGS="$CXXFLAGS -I/usr/local/opt/libomp/include"
export LDFLAGS="$LDFLAGS -Wl,-rpath,/usr/local/opt/libomp/lib -L/usr/local/opt/libomp/lib -lomp"

FLAML::::.github/workflows/python-package.yml::::jobs::::build::::steps::::steps_3::::run::::python -m pip install --upgrade pip wheel
pip install -e .
python -c "import flaml"
pip install -e .[test]

FLAML::::.github/workflows/python-package.yml::::jobs::::build::::steps::::steps_5::::run::::# stop the build if there are Python syntax errors or undefined names
flake8 . --count --select=E9,F63,F7,F82 --show-source --statistics
# exit-zero treats all errors as warnings. The GitHub editor is 127 chars wide
flake8 . --count --exit-zero --max-complexity=10 --max-line-length=127 --statistics
